# Project 4 - due Feb 7


## GOALS

Build a class planner page that support your development efforts.


### Tools
* Bluehost
* Github & Github Desktop
* Brackets & Firefox
* Filezilla
* Screen Capture


### Web Pages
* bacs200/index.html
* bacs200/04/index.html


### HTML
* Basic HTML template
* h1, h2, ul, li, p, a, img
* Images & Hyperlinks
* Lists & Tables


### Screenshots (in "bacs200/04/images")
* "ftp-site-manager.png" - Site Manager
* "ftp-dirs.png" - FTP Default Directories
* "ftp-files.png" - FTP Files
* "github-website.png" - Show repo at Github
* "git-clone.png" - Github Desktop showing your clone
* "bluehost.png" - Show the Advanced tab of the Bluehost control panel
* "file-explorer.png" - Show the Windows files with your repo
* "brackets.png" - Brackets showing Open Folder and Beatify


