## STEPS

### Capture Screenshots
* Create screenshots (8 images)


### Create Project Page
* Make page at "04/index.html"


### Image with Thumbnail
* Embed small image in page
* Link to full size image
* See [Demo Server](https://unco-bacs.org/bacs200/04/) for demo of screenshots


### Create Table (2 columns, 8 rows)
* Label for Screenshot
* Thumbnail of image (200 pixels in width)
* Link to full size image


## REQUIREMENTS
* Home Page updated with Project 4
* Project 4 Page exists (04/index.html)
* Table of Images (table, tr, td)
* Thumbnail/Full Size Pattern
* Thumbnail and Full Size Images
* Screenshots (in "images" directory)
* Screenshots in Github repo
* Screenshots show correct contents
* Use HTML tags - h1, h2, ul, li, p, a, img, ul, li
* Page contains valid HTML


